Trip Plan Swiss (Europe)

Hari 1 – Zurich Arrival & City Tour
09.00 – Tiba di Zurich Airport → ambil Swiss Travel Pass di bandara.
10.00 – Naik kereta S-Bahn ke Zurich HB (stasiun utama).
10.30 – 12.00 – Check-in hotel & simpan barang.
12.30 – Makan siang di restoran lokal (misal: Zeughauskeller, menu khas Swiss).
13.30 – 17.00 – Explore Old Town (Altstadt), Bahnhofstrasse, Grossmünster.
17.30 – Jalan sore di Danau Zurich → bisa naik kapal ferry singkat.
19.00 – Dinner di tepi danau (misal: LakeSide Restaurant).
21.00 – Balik hotel, istirahat.

Hari 2 – Zurich → Luzern → Mount Pilatus
07.00 – Breakfast hotel.
08.00 – Naik kereta Zurich HB → Luzern (1 jam).
09.30 – Tiba di Luzern, titip koper di hotel.
10.00 – 12.00 – Explore kota: Chapel Bridge, Lion Monument.
12.30 – Lunch di Rathaus Brauerei (restoran lokal tepi sungai).
13.30 – 17.30 – Naik ke Mount Pilatus:
                Luzern → Alpnachstad (kereta 20 menit)
                Kereta cogwheel ke Pilatus Kulm (30 menit, kereta curam banget).
                Explore panorama, foto, kopi sore di atas gunung.
18.00 – Turun via gondola ke Kriens → bus kembali ke Luzern.
19.30 – Dinner di hotel/Old Town.
21.00 – Istirahat.

Hari 3 – Luzern → Interlaken → Lauterbrunnen
07.00 – Breakfast, check-out.
08.00 – Kereta Luzern → Interlaken (2 jam, via Brünig Pass, pemandangan bagus).
10.30 – Tiba Interlaken, taruh koper di hotel.
11.00 – Naik kereta Interlaken → Lauterbrunnen (20 menit).
11.30 – 15.00 – Jalan-jalan Lauterbrunnen: Staubbach Falls, Trümmelbach Falls.
12.30 – Lunch di Hotel Oberland (menu lokal).
15.30 – Opsional: naik gondola ke Mürren/Wengen (desa pegunungan).
18.00 – Balik ke Interlaken.
19.00 – Dinner di Husi Bierhaus (menu Swiss + internasional).
21.00 – Istirahat.

Hari 4 – Interlaken → Jungfraujoch (Top of Europe)
06.30 – Breakfast pagi.
07.30 – Kereta Interlaken → Lauterbrunnen → Kleine Scheidegg → Jungfraujoch (3 jam total).
11.00 – 14.00 – Explore Jungfraujoch: Ice Palace, Sphinx Observatory, foto salju.
12.30 – Lunch di restoran Top of Europe.
14.30 – Turun kembali ke Interlaken (3 jam).
18.00 – Jalan sore di Interlaken, shopping souvenir.
19.30 – Dinner di Little Thai (kalau bosan masakan Swiss).
21.00 – Balik hotel.
